1
00:00:09,114 --> 00:00:13,160
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

2
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:17,800
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

3
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:22,840
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

4
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:28,000
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

5
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:32,415
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

6
00:00:32,415 --> 00:00:37,167
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

7
00:00:37,167 --> 00:00:42,400
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

8
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:47,853
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪

9
00:00:50,820 --> 00:00:55,760
=Rise Again=

10
00:00:56,144 --> 00:00:58,878
=Episode 15=

11
00:01:00,560 --> 00:01:01,359
Su Wubing!

12
00:01:01,960 --> 00:01:02,439
Come with me.

13
00:01:07,120 --> 00:01:08,239
- Su Wubing!
- Su Wubing!

14
00:01:09,359 --> 00:01:11,239
The tournament is about to begin.

15
00:01:11,560 --> 00:01:13,280
Everyone, please step forward.

16
00:01:13,840 --> 00:01:14,319
Mr. Ye.

17
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:25,319
(Su Wubing...)

18
00:01:25,319 --> 00:01:27,040
(What else are you hiding from me?)

19
00:01:27,599 --> 00:01:28,439
(Didn't expect)

20
00:01:28,439 --> 00:01:30,319
(Su Wubing has so many women
around him.)

21
00:01:30,959 --> 00:01:32,680
(With all these women around,)

22
00:01:32,680 --> 00:01:34,120
(why does he still
act so high and mighty?)

23
00:01:37,760 --> 00:01:39,120
Why did the tournament

24
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:41,439
drawn so many people from Fan City?

25
00:01:42,760 --> 00:01:44,159
My Lord.

26
00:01:45,959 --> 00:01:48,359
Ever since the Heavenly God Sword
fell into the mortal world,

27
00:01:49,519 --> 00:01:52,680
it has stood atop
the Two Realms Mountain.

28
00:01:53,959 --> 00:01:55,560
And so this mountain

29
00:01:55,959 --> 00:01:58,159
has been infused
with immense spiritual power.

30
00:01:59,079 --> 00:02:02,159
People come
seeking the power of the sword,

31
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:04,400
but the mountain gate

32
00:02:04,799 --> 00:02:07,959
opens only once every twenty years.

33
00:02:09,159 --> 00:02:10,159
Twenty years?

34
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:11,159
Yes.

35
00:02:12,759 --> 00:02:15,520
A mortal's lifespan is limited.

36
00:02:16,639 --> 00:02:17,439
So

37
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:20,319
whenever the gate opens,

38
00:02:20,639 --> 00:02:22,360
they flock to it.

39
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:24,319
All of them hoping

40
00:02:25,159 --> 00:02:27,560
to pull out the divine sword
and rule the world.

41
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:30,080
Interesting.

42
00:02:33,759 --> 00:02:35,080
(If I retrieve the Heavenly God Sword,)

43
00:02:35,479 --> 00:02:37,360
(I'll have a real chance
against the Heavenly Dao.)

44
00:02:44,639 --> 00:02:45,280
Fang Tian?

45
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:47,680
(Why is she here?)

46
00:02:48,039 --> 00:02:50,439
My Lord, time is running out.

47
00:03:07,039 --> 00:03:07,560
Grandpa.

48
00:03:09,639 --> 00:03:10,439
(Fang Xianglin)
My girl.

49
00:03:10,439 --> 00:03:11,309
(Head of Fang family)

50
00:03:11,479 --> 00:03:13,280
You finally came to see me.

51
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:14,960
I was just thinking

52
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:16,680
if you kept refusing,

53
00:03:16,879 --> 00:03:18,639
I'd go to the Su family myself
and bring you back.

54
00:03:18,759 --> 00:03:20,240
Come on, sit.

55
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:22,879
It's not that I don't want to go back.

56
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:25,360
Mom just got better.

57
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:26,680
I want to stay with her longer.

58
00:03:29,120 --> 00:03:30,360
You're not ready to return?

59
00:03:33,080 --> 00:03:34,080
Silly girl,

60
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:36,719
I won't force you.

61
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:39,360
But remember this,

62
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:41,919
you will always be a daughter
of the Fang family.

63
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:44,000
Whenever you want to come back,

64
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:45,639
you're always welcome.

65
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:48,159
Thank you, Grandpa.

66
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:50,240
I called you here today

67
00:03:50,479 --> 00:03:52,120
not just to see you,

68
00:03:53,080 --> 00:03:55,120
but also to test

69
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:56,960
this Su Wubing you like.

70
00:03:57,319 --> 00:03:58,879
See what kind of man he really is.

71
00:03:59,159 --> 00:04:00,000
Grandpa.

72
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:02,240
I see him

73
00:04:02,639 --> 00:04:04,439
as a brother.

74
00:04:04,759 --> 00:04:05,719
Silly girl.

75
00:04:06,199 --> 00:04:07,439
I can see

76
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:08,840
right through you.

77
00:04:11,159 --> 00:04:12,039
Don't worry.

78
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:14,319
I don't mind you two staying in touch.

79
00:04:14,479 --> 00:04:15,639
I just want to see

80
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:18,439
if he is really capable enough.

81
00:04:19,319 --> 00:04:21,079
So what do you think of him?

82
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:35,360
Over the years,

83
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:40,040
many have stood out at the tournament.

84
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:42,279
But in the end,

85
00:04:42,279 --> 00:04:45,399
no one has ever managed
to pull out that divine sword.

86
00:04:46,319 --> 00:04:49,199
Is Su Wubing really that strong?

87
00:05:21,839 --> 00:05:22,560
Where's Grandfather?

88
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:23,920
Wasn't he with you?

89
00:05:24,959 --> 00:05:26,160
I sent him to handle something.

90
00:05:26,680 --> 00:05:28,759
So you'll represent the Ye family.

91
00:05:33,279 --> 00:05:35,480
The tournament is about to begin!

92
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:36,879
Present your treasures!

93
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:47,759
Zhang family
presents the Nine Heavens Star Map,

94
00:05:47,759 --> 00:05:49,319
granted entry to the Heavenly Steps.

95
00:05:58,959 --> 00:06:01,160
Li family
presents South Sea Mystic Mirror,

96
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:02,519
granted entry to the Mystic Steps.

97
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:08,439
Sir, our Xue family is not
what it used to be.

98
00:06:08,519 --> 00:06:10,160
We really don't have anything
worthy to offer.

99
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:11,759
Could you please make an exception

100
00:06:11,759 --> 00:06:13,160
and let us in to take a look?

101
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:16,319
If we can rise again
through this tournament,

102
00:06:16,519 --> 00:06:17,680
we will repay you handsomely.

103
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:19,079
The Xue family is not admitted.

104
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:20,279
Please wait for the next cycle.

105
00:06:20,759 --> 00:06:21,759
Another twenty years?

106
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:22,199
This...

107
00:06:26,680 --> 00:06:27,920
What kind of rule is that?

108
00:06:28,959 --> 00:06:30,839
They say it's to show sincerity
through offerings,

109
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:32,959
but it's just screening people.

110
00:06:49,519 --> 00:06:50,839
Isn't that Su Wubing?

111
00:06:51,879 --> 00:06:52,959
Why is he standing over there?

112
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:54,759
No treasure, no entry.

113
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:57,240
Some people

114
00:06:57,319 --> 00:06:59,279
have just never seen the world.

115
00:06:59,519 --> 00:07:01,319
Still want to enter the summit plaza?

116
00:07:01,959 --> 00:07:04,720
They just don't know their places.

117
00:07:05,319 --> 00:07:06,680
Whether we can enter it

118
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:08,480
is none of your business.

119
00:07:08,639 --> 00:07:09,639
You already

120
00:07:09,839 --> 00:07:11,360
suffered losses at the martial hall,

121
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:12,560
and you still dare come again.

122
00:07:14,959 --> 00:07:16,480
I go wherever I want.

123
00:07:16,759 --> 00:07:17,839
That's none of your business.

124
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:20,360
Instead of worrying about others,

125
00:07:20,680 --> 00:07:22,160
worry about yourself.

126
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,120
Look at the Xue family.

127
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:26,519
That will be the Lin family's fate.

128
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:28,279
Gu Yuanbing.

129
00:07:28,519 --> 00:07:30,519
Your family is really overreaching.

130
00:07:31,360 --> 00:07:32,560
And who are you supposed to be?

131
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:34,639
Ye Xiaonuan of the Herbal Hall.

132
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,519
Ye Tianmiao is my grandfather.

133
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:39,920
So it's the granddaughter
of that old man.

134
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:41,959
My apologies then.

135
00:07:43,160 --> 00:07:44,040
However,

136
00:07:44,399 --> 00:07:46,560
I'll give you a friendly reminder,

137
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:47,759
out of respect for your charm.

138
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:49,759
Try not to hang around people like him.

139
00:07:50,079 --> 00:07:51,439
You'll only lower yourself.

140
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:55,959
What?

141
00:07:56,759 --> 00:07:58,240
Let me warn you, Su Wubing.

142
00:07:58,639 --> 00:08:00,160
This is not a place

143
00:08:00,879 --> 00:08:02,519
where you can run wild.

144
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:04,399
Mr. Gu.

145
00:08:04,959 --> 00:08:06,759
He's just a country bumpkin.

146
00:08:08,040 --> 00:08:10,079
Even if he's become
the Lin family's son-in-law,

147
00:08:10,279 --> 00:08:12,079
he still doesn't belong in high society.

148
00:08:14,079 --> 00:08:14,439
Let's go.

149
00:08:24,759 --> 00:08:26,160
Today, our Gu family is here

150
00:08:26,639 --> 00:08:28,040
not only to present a rare treasure,

151
00:08:28,319 --> 00:08:30,639
but also to contribute
our Gu Group's industries,

152
00:08:30,959 --> 00:08:33,720
as our way of supporting
Two Realms Mountain.

153
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:53,039
So many treasures.

154
00:08:56,679 --> 00:08:58,559
Gu Group is granted entry
to the Earth Steps.

155
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:22,240
Lin family presents a jade pendant,
granted entry to the Heavenly Steps.

156
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:27,039
Wait!

157
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:30,159
Where is his treasure?

158
00:09:30,759 --> 00:09:31,679
Why is he allowed in?

159
00:09:32,039 --> 00:09:34,240
Exactly, no treasure, no entry.

160
00:09:35,039 --> 00:09:36,360
He came with me.

161
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:37,440
He's part of the Lin family.

162
00:09:38,559 --> 00:09:40,559
So just because he came with you,
he's a Lin now?

163
00:09:41,159 --> 00:09:42,279
How do you prove that?

164
00:09:42,679 --> 00:09:43,720
You're not even married.

165
00:09:46,240 --> 00:09:47,559
My grandfather can prove it.

166
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:50,080
Miss Ye,

167
00:09:50,559 --> 00:09:52,519
even if your grandfather
is the Medical Saint,

168
00:09:52,759 --> 00:09:54,360
even if his healing skills
are unmatched,

169
00:09:54,960 --> 00:09:56,559
his words don't carry

170
00:09:56,879 --> 00:09:59,360
much weight here.

171
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:01,159
Where's your confidence from?

172
00:10:01,759 --> 00:10:04,039
More importantly,
Su Wubing is absolutely...

173
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:06,960
Absolutely what?

174
00:10:07,519 --> 00:10:08,759
Lost for words now, are you?

175
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:10,159
Sir.

176
00:10:10,799 --> 00:10:12,720
If someone tries to force their way,

177
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:14,519
according to the rules,

178
00:10:14,759 --> 00:10:16,120
how should they be dealt with?

179
00:10:16,879 --> 00:10:18,720
The tournament gathers all heroes.

180
00:10:18,720 --> 00:10:20,080
If one lacks true skill,

181
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:21,360
please step out of the gate.

182
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:23,759
What nonsense is this?

183
00:10:24,279 --> 00:10:25,759
He's Lin family's son-in-law.

184
00:10:25,799 --> 00:10:26,759
No question about it.

185
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:28,759
It's fine.

186
00:10:29,679 --> 00:10:30,480
Sir.

187
00:10:31,159 --> 00:10:32,360
Except offering treasures,

188
00:10:32,759 --> 00:10:35,159
is there any other way
to enter the gate?

189
00:10:36,120 --> 00:10:36,519
Yes.

190
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:38,240
We have five kinds of steps.

191
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:40,480
The Heaven, Earth, Mystic,
and Yellow Steps require treasures.

192
00:10:40,600 --> 00:10:42,600
The middle steps
are the Ascending Immortal Steps.

193
00:10:42,799 --> 00:10:44,559
If an ordinary person tries to take it,

194
00:10:44,559 --> 00:10:46,360
they'll feel mountains
pressing down on them.

195
00:10:46,360 --> 00:10:48,519
If you truly have skill
to climb this tier,

196
00:10:48,519 --> 00:10:49,679
you won't need any treasure.

197
00:10:50,360 --> 00:10:51,000
Su Wubing.

198
00:10:51,639 --> 00:10:53,759
Why don't you go in first?

199
00:10:54,080 --> 00:10:55,120
I'll wait here for you.

200
00:10:56,679 --> 00:10:57,279
What now?

201
00:10:57,720 --> 00:10:58,240
Scared?

202
00:10:58,919 --> 00:11:00,559
If you've got nothing, get lost.

203
00:11:01,320 --> 00:11:01,799
It's fine.

204
00:11:32,025 --> 00:11:36,128
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

205
00:11:36,128 --> 00:11:40,848
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

206
00:11:40,848 --> 00:11:45,728
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

207
00:11:45,728 --> 00:11:50,848
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

208
00:11:50,848 --> 00:11:55,248
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

209
00:11:55,248 --> 00:11:59,928
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

210
00:11:59,928 --> 00:12:05,328
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

211
00:12:05,328 --> 00:12:11,722
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪
